; bios_hello.flld — Flommodore Linker Description (Phase 8 8.5)
;
; Identical placement to hello.flld: code AT $04100 puts the .flapp's
; FB header exactly where the BIOS autoboot scan looks (§6.9 /
; amendment 2.3), so `--autoboot` runs this program at power-on.

ENTRY start              ; entry point symbol name

SECTION code AT $04100   ; place code at the start of free RAM
SECTION data AFTER code  ; data immediately after code
SECTION bss  AFTER data  ; zero-initialised space after that
